 purchased Pareja from Independiente Medellín; Pareja paid immediate dividends, helping Cali to a championship in the 1995-<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../636/34636.xml">
1996</link> season, their first in 22 years.  He would stay with them four years, before signing with <association wordnetid="108049401" confidence="0.8">
<event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
<social_event wordnetid="107288639" confidence="0.8">
