, playing 11 games and scoring three goals, and playing in the (Catalan). Pareja is nicknamed <it>El Generalito</it>, the Little <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../537/148537.xml">
General</link>, but is now called <it>Papi</it>.</p>



